<l>niṇantīyi liṭṭaṉṉa neñciṉārk kuṇṭō </l>
<l>puṇarntūṭi niṟpō meṉal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it possible for those whose hearts melt like fat in the fire to say they can feign a strong dislike and remain so?</l>
